Southampton assumed Cedric would be moving to a lower level or abroad. When he picked up the injury there was an acceptance he could go for free. They saw barely any logic in the approach and put it down to certain relationships between #afc and Soares&rsquo;s people. [<br />
@TheAthleticUK<br />
]

Mathieu Debuchy on Saliba: &quot;'He's a great player. I'm so happy for him to play next season for a big club like Arsenal. He improves every game &amp; I think he is a great player. He's strong with good technique. He's quick. I think he has a lot of quality to play at #Arsenal&quot;<br />
<br />
Yohan Cabaye on Saliba: &quot;He's like a big man - he's only 18 but he's like a big man. He's strong &amp; hopefully he will adapt himself really quickly. In a club like #Arsenal with French players, I think he can do really well&quot;

